Package jogosolimpicos

Provides the classes necessary to manages the data of the olympic games.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Atleta
    Main class of Athlete.
    CodigosPais
    Main class for the historical of the IOC codes for the countries.
    Disciplina
    Main class of the generic competition.
    Equipa
    Main class of the teams of athletes for the team competitions.
    JogosOlimpicos
    Main class for the edition of the Olympic Games.
    Listagem
    Main class to create the reports for the application.
    Medalhas
    Main class of the management of the medals.
    Modalidade
    Main class of the sport.
    Pais
    Main class of the country.
    Prova
    Main class for the competition with a year.
    ProvaCol
    Main class for the team competition with a year.
    ProvaInd
    Main class for the individual competition in this year.
    ResultadosCol
    Main class for the team results
    ResultadosInd
    Main class for individual result.
